 <title class="- topic/title " xtrf="/Users/scottb/Documents/git/documentation/admin_guide/policies_samples.dita" xtrc="title:1">Sample Policies</title>
 <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc " xtrc="shortdesc:1" xtrf="/Users/scottb/Documents/git/documentation/admin_guide/policies_samples.dita">A few example use cases and associated policies.</shortdesc>
